description: The Hike is long along the ridge once you are up there but the views of the many glaciers across the valley are great and the view into Revelstoke BC.
directions: At Three Valley  heading east turn onto Three Valley Victor Forest Service Road  Lat 50.936756° Long -118.432352°.  and it is 12 km approx. to the trail head Lat  50.942747° Long -118.345862°.
title: Mount MacPherson West Approach
